thread.title: Fingerprint key to bomb suspect ID, capture
thread.title_full: Fingerprint key to bomb suspect ID, capture

author: Don Scotter
text: Look at this. Doesn't this just reassure you to the max that the government has its stuff together and would thoroughly vet all these thousands of Muslims it plans to bring here? Complete inexcusable incompetence. A lot of heads should roll for this. But they won't. That only happens in the private sector which has accountability and self respect. "The U.S. government has mistakenly granted citizenship to at least 858 immigrants from countries of concern to national security or with high rates of immigration fraud who had pending deportation orders" http://www.cbsnews.com/news/more-than-800-immigrants-accidentally-granted-u-s-citizenship/
